README groff

    PAPERSIZE

    As of groff version 1.22.2 release 2 the default papersize for
    groff can be defined in /etc/papersize.  Just add the required
    papersize like 'letter' or 'a4' here, default is 'letter'.

    See
    http://www.gnu.org/software/groff/manual/html_node/DESC-File-Format.html
    for more informations.

End of file.
